Dialogue: 0,00:00:28.14,00:00:30.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个地方他妈烂透了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}is that this place sucks donkey dick.
Dialogue: 0,00:00:31.75,00:00:34.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,崔克斯法官指定我作为威尔斯小姐的监督人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Judge Trakes appointed me Miss Wells' conservator.
Dialogue: 0,00:00:34.30,00:00:35.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好  亲爱的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hello, darling.
Dialogue: 0,00:00:35.70,00:00:38.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你妻子的行为能力也许有所下降\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your wife's capacity may be diminished,
