Dialogue: 0,00:00:40.97,00:00:42.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,转移  误导\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Distract. Misdirect.
Dialogue: 0,00:00:42.82,00:00:46.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让他们关注我们说什么是最重要的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Make them give a fuck about what we say is important.
Dialogue: 0,00:00:52.98,00:00:56.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快来找我  影·穆恩\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come find me, Shadow Moon.
Dialogue: 0,00:01:17.22,00:01:20.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,国父们信奉一位造物主\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Founders believed in a creator
Dialogue: 0,00:01:20.36,00:01:25.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他赋予了每个人平等和自由\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}who endowed every individual with equality and freedom.
Dialogue: 0,00:01:25.29,00:01:28.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美国对这一点深信不疑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}America was conceived around that truth
Dialogue: 0,00:01:28.04,00:01:31.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而「独立宣言」就是对这位造物主的誓言\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and the Declaration was an oath to that creator.
Dialogue: 0,00:01:33.08,00:01:35.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,庄严承诺这个新政府\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A solemn promise that this new government
Dialogue: 0,00:01:35.91,00:01:39.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会维护其公民的神圣权利\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}would ensure the divine rights of its citizens.
Dialogue: 0,00:01:39.84,00:01:43.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,包括生命  自由  以及追求幸福的权利\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Life, liberty, and a shot at happiness.
Dialogue: 0,00:01:45.44,00:01:48.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但这个新政府负债累累\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But the new government was overrun with debt.
